Deny execution of PHP files in uploads directory
<Directory "uploads/">
<FilesMatch ".(php|php5|php7|phps)$">
Order allow,deny
Deny from all
</FilesMatch>
</Directory>

Disable directory listing
Options -Indexes

Block access to sensitive files
<FilesMatch "^(.env|config.php|composer.json|composer.lock)$">
Order allow,deny
Deny from all
</FilesMatch>

Prevent access to this .htaccess file itself
<Files .htaccess>
Order allow,deny
Deny from all
</Files>

Enable CORS for API access (optional)
<IfModule mod_headers.c> Header set Access-Control-Allow-Origin "*" </IfModule>